    <para id="import-auto-id3080460">List all the possible values of <m:math><m:semantics><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mi>s</m:mi></m:mrow><m:mrow/></m:mrow><m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{s} {}</m:annotation></m:semantics></m:math> and <m:math><m:semantics><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:msub><m:mi>m</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mi>s</m:mi></m:mrow></m:msub></m:mrow><m:mrow/></m:mrow><m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{m rSub { size 8{s} } } {}</m:annotation></m:semantics></m:math> for an electron. Are there particles for which these values are different? The same?</para>
